cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.DS 

This paper deals with online learning algorithms for multiclass classification with partial feedback. The problem is related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, which are covered by cs.LG and cs.AI. The paper also mentions applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL), indicating that these sub-categories are relevant. Finally, the algorithm proposed in the paper is based on a margin-based approach, which is a common technique in machine learning and optimization, suggesting that cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) may also be a relevant sub-category.
